**Horsemen Team**
The Horsemen win when all players are either dead, unaligned or part of the Horsemen team. Members of the Horsemen Team do not know each other at the start of the game.

__Roles__
Apocalyptic Horseman (T)
Horseman
Horseman of Death
Horseman of Famine
Horseman of Pestilence
Horseman of War

__Formalized__
Win Condition: @(Alignment:Horsemen), @(Class:Unaligned)
